---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — ajscanlan.dev" description="Working notebook — engineering, writing, and the space between.">
    <div class="layout-post about-wrap">

        <div class="avail-pill">
            <span class="green-dot"></span>
            Available for new roles · Jun 2026
        </div>

        <h1 class="about-h1">A.J. Scanlan</h1>

        <p class="about-lede">
            Senior software engineer. I build reliable systems, write clearly about how they work,
            and bring the same rigor to both. Based in NYC.
        </p>

        <div class="about-grid">
            <span class="grid-label">Currently</span>
            <span class="grid-value">Open to senior IC and tech-lead roles — distributed systems, developer tooling, or product engineering at a company doing something that matters.</span>

            <span class="grid-label">Background</span>
            <span class="grid-value">Mobile engineer turned full-stack. Spent several years building production iOS apps, then shifted toward TypeScript, distributed systems, and platform work. I care about correctness, legibility, and shipping.</span>

            <span class="grid-label">How I work</span>
            <span class="grid-value">Prefer async, written communication. Ship iteratively, document why not just what, and flag risks early. I've worked in small startups and larger product teams — I adapt, but I write and read a lot either way.</span>

            <span class="grid-label">Stack</span>
            <span class="grid-value stack-value">
                <span class="chip chip-filled">TypeScript</span>
                <span class="chip chip-filled">React</span>
                <span class="chip chip-filled">Astro</span>
                <span class="chip chip-filled">Swift</span>
                <span class="chip chip-muted">Python</span>
                <span class="chip chip-muted">PostgreSQL</span>
                <span class="chip chip-muted">Node</span>
            </span>

            <span class="grid-label">Reach me</span>
            <span class="grid-value">
                <a href="mailto:hi@ajscanlan.dev" class="reach-link">hi@ajscanlan.dev</a>
                <span class="reach-sep">·</span>
                <a href="https://github.com/AJScanlan" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="reach-link">GitHub</a>
            </span>

            <span class="grid-label">This site</span>
            <span class="grid-value">Astro 5 · TypeScript · Tailwind · MDX · hosted on Vercel</span>
        </div>

    </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
    .about-wrap {
        padding-top: 64px;
        padding-bottom: 80px;
    }

    .avail-pill {
        display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
        font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
        font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        color: var(--ink-400); margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .green-dot {
        width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: #1f7a5c; flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .about-h1 {
        font-size: 2.75rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: -0.025em;
        line-height: 1.08;
        color: var(--ink-900);
        margin: 0 0 14px;
    }

    .about-lede {
        font-size: 1.1875rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: var(--ink-600);
        max-width: 60ch;
        margin: 0 0 36px;
    }

    .about-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 140px 1fr;
        gap: 0 40px;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--ink-100);
    }

    .grid-label {
        font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 500;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        color: var(--ink-400);
        padding: 16px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink-100);
        align-self: start;
    }

    .grid-value {
        font-size: 13.5px;
        color: var(--ink-700);
        padding: 16px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink-100);
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .stack-value {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 4px;
        align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .chip {
        font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
        font-size: 10px;
        border-radius: 3px;
        padding: 2px 7px;
        display: inline-block;
    }
    .chip-filled { background: var(--ink-900); color: var(--paper); }
    .chip-muted  { background: var(--paper-2); color: var(--ink-600); }

    .reach-link {
        color: var(--ink-900);
        text-decoration: none;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink-200);
    }
    .reach-link:hover { color: var(--fox-ink); border-bottom-color: var(--fox-ink); }
    .reach-sep { margin: 0 6px; color: var(--ink-300); }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
        .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        .grid-label { padding-bottom: 4px; border-bottom: 0; }
    }
</style>
